OL,3,CLyra McKee murder trial hears mobile
OL,4,Cphone evidence is 'degraded and
OL,5,Cunreliable'
OL,7,FThe strength of evidence against a man
OL,8,Fjointly charged with the murder of
OL,9,Fjournalist Lyra McKee has been
OL,10,Fquestioned by his defence barrister.
OL,12,FThe 29-year-old author died after
OL,13,Fbeing hit by a bullet as she stood
OL,14,Fclose to police vehicles while
OL,15,Fobserving disturbances in the Creggan
OL,16,Farea of Londonderry on April 18, 2019.
OL,18,FIt came as an MTV crew were filming in
OL,19,Fthe area for a documentary.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
