CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776348651
OL,3,CLyra McKee murder trial hears mobile
OL,4,Cphone evidence is 'degraded and
OL,5,Cunreliable'
OL,7,FSeveral petrol bombs had been directed
OL,8,Fat police and a car was set on fire
OL,9,Fduring chaotic scenes which culminated
OL,10,Fin four shots being fired towards
OL,11,Fofficers, which the prosecution
OL,12,Fcontend were aimed and deliberate.
OL,14,FThe New IRA claimed responsibility for
OL,15,Fthe death of Ms McKee.
OL,17,FPaul McIntyre, 58, of Kells Walk in
OL,18,FDerry, Peter Cavanagh, 37, of Mary
OL,19,FStreet, and Jordan Gareth Devine, 25,
OL,20,Fof Bishop Street, are facing a joint
OL,21,Fenterprise murder charge.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
