OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776348651
OL,3,CLyra McKee murder trial hears mobile
OL,4,Cphone evidence is 'degraded and
OL,5,Cunreliable'
OL,7,FThey are also facing other charges
OL,8,Fconnected to the shooting and the
OL,9,Frioting.
OL,11,FSix other Derry men are facing charges
OL,12,Fincluding rioting and throwing petrol
OL,13,Fbombs in the non-jury trial.
OL,15,FAnother man accused of rioting and
OL,16,Fthrowing petrol bombs on the night of
OL,17,Fthe murder died during trial
OL,18,Fproceedings last year.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
