CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776348651
OL,3,CLyra McKee murder trial hears mobile
OL,4,Cphone evidence is 'degraded and
OL,5,Cunreliable'
OL,7,FIt is the prosecution's case that the
OL,8,Fthree men accused of murder had
OL,9,Faccompanied a lone gunman to the
OL,10,Ffiring point on the night and
OL,11,Fencouraged or assisted him.
OL,13,FThey have all denied the charges and
OL,14,Frefused to give evidence.
OL,16,FIn closing submissions made across two
OL,17,Fdays in March before the Easter break,
OL,18,Fthe prosecution said the three have
OL,19,Fbeen linked to the scene by clothing
OL,20,Fand physical features.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
