PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776348651
OL,3,CLyra McKee murder trial hears mobile
OL,4,Cphone evidence is 'degraded and
OL,5,Cunreliable'
OL,7,FThe court has been hearing closing
OL,8,Fsubmissions from barristers
OL,9,Frepresenting the defendants this week.
OL,11,FOn Wednesday afternoon, Mark
OL,12,FMulholland KC took issue with the
OL,13,Fquality of footage used in the
OL,14,Fprosecution case.
OL,16,FThe prosecution, which contends
OL,17,FMcIntyre played a "leading role",
OL,18,Flinked him with Person D seen in the
OL,19,Ffootage.
OL,26,@yD@SOUyD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
