FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776348651
OL,3,CLyra McKee murder trial hears mobile
OL,4,Cphone evidence is 'degraded and
OL,5,Cunreliable'
OL,7,FMr Mulholland told Judge Patricia
OL,8,FSmyth the prosecution's closing had
OL,9,F"not properly reflected the state of
OL,10,Fthe evidence", and said mobile phone
OL,11,Ffootage of the shooting had been taken
OL,12,Ffrom social media and the quality was
OL,13,F"degraded".
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@MO]uD@AOUuD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776348651
OL,3,CLyra McKee murder trial hears mobile
OL,4,Cphone evidence is 'degraded and
OL,5,Cunreliable'
OL,7,F"This arises due to compression, it's
OL,8,Fthe loss of pixels, the detail in the
OL,9,Ffootage, and that is the type of
OL,10,Fcompromised image that this court is
OL,11,Fbeing invited as the grounding
OL,12,Fevidential foundation to come to a
OL,13,Fconclusion beyond reasonable doubt as
OL,14,Fthe evidence for a murder charge," he
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776348651
OL,3,CLyra McKee murder trial hears mobile
OL,4,Cphone evidence is 'degraded and
OL,5,Cunreliable'
OL,7,F"The footage simply does not pass
OL,8,Fmuster, and if the court accepts that
OL,9,Fthen in terms of the murder charge, it
OL,10,Fgoes no further. There is no other
OL,11,Fsupporting evidence that can salvage
OL,12,Fthe wholly degraded and therefore
OL,13,Funreliable imagery being relied upon."
OL,15,FMr Mulholland's submission on behalf
OL,16,Fof McIntyre is expected to resume on
OL,17,FThursday morning.
OL,19,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,20,FITVX
